ygData.messageBody:
That makes me wonder......what does tundra jack carry?

Vashi, Eternal warriors

>
>From: "Jones, Brian" <brian.jones@...>
>
>Yeah unfortunately for you evil types all the entrances to the plains are
>guarded by NPCs. You need invisibility to get past some of them. Then
>you have Tundra Jack and Iceberg the Polar Bear (I saw Iceberg take out
>a Wooly Mammoth in two swipes!). He roams the plains too so he would
>probably attack you. A shaman barbarian friend of mine accidently walked
>up to him with autoattack on and got hit twice for 180 and 176 damage
>(before Iceberg had a chance to take a step forward).
